<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <div class="faq">
          <h3 class="faq__heading">Will the app work in 2019?</h3>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>Yes.</p>
          </div>
          <p>
            <a href="#"><small>Back to top</small></a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq">
          <h3 class="faq__heading">How does this awesome app work?</h3>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              This wonderful app automagically syncs your Strava cycle activities to kilometrikisa.fi, which means less
              time inputting boring KMs and more time out with your bike!
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            <a href="#"><small>Back to top</small></a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq">
          <h3 class="faq__heading">How often does this app sync?</h3>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>Once a day.</p>
          </div>
          <p>
            <a href="#"><small>Back to top</small></a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq">
          <h3 class="faq__heading">What does this app sync?</h3>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              All of your cycling activities from the last five days. It overwrites all your entries on Kilometrikisa.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            <a href="#"><small>Back to top</small></a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq">
          <h3 class="faq__heading">What do I need to do?</h3>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              Simply follow the instructions on the <a href="/">homepage</a> to get started, will take less than one
              minute! All you have to do is authorize our Strava app, enter your kilometrikisa.fi details and let the
              app do the rest.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            <a href="#"><small>Back to top</small></a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq">
          <h3 class="faq__heading">Having some issues?</h3>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              If you experience any issues, or have any cool ideas for this project you can open an issue on
              <a href="https://www.github.com/tumetsu/strava2kilometrikisa" target="_blank">project's Github repository</a>
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            <a href="#"><small>Back to top</small></a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

